前男友
Old boyfriend.

392
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:09,750
听说他之后办过无数次喜酒
I hear the weddings go on forever.

393
00:20:09,970 --> 00:20:13,010
喜酒的时间比婚姻还长  这笑话能乐一辈子
Longer than the marriages, so goes the joke.

394
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:17,910
本尼特先生需要你帮他查一个人
Mr. Bennett needs you to look into something for him.

395
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:21,470
我与马吉德·贾瓦迪合作  不是利兰·本尼特
My arrangement's with Majid Javadi, not Leland Bennett.

396
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:22,620
没错
Correct.

397
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:24,270
但本尼特先生今天得到的消息
But what Mr. Bennett heard today

398
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:26,210
