might reverberate onto you.

399
00:20:26,610 --> 00:20:27,630
牵连我
Onto me?

400
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,490
需要我提醒你吗
Do I need to remind you--

401
00:20:29,490 --> 00:20:31,670
你已被外国政府招募为特工
You're a recruited agent of a foreign government?

402
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:35,830
我见过贾瓦迪  一次而已
I met with Javadi. Once.

403
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:38,440
我同意做他的顾问  而不是做特工
I agreed to consult with him. I'm nobody's agent.

404
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,890
不知道中情局能否理解其中的区别
I doubt the CIA would appreciate the distinction.

405
00:20:40,890 --> 00:20:42,140
你得到什么消息了
What the hell do you know about it?

406
00:20:42,140 --> 00:20:43,950
我知道本律所因为某些原因
I know the law firm appears to be

407
00:20:43,950 --> 00:20:46,690
成为了被质询的目标
the target of an inquiry of some kind.

408
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:50,810
这个我可不知道
Well, not one that I'm aware of.

409
00:20:51,450 --> 00:20:53,450
这个警告是经私人渠道传出来的
The warning was delivered personally,

410
00:20:53,450 --> 00:20:55,370
没通过官方渠道
outside of official channels.

411
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:57,490
是在局里工作的人吗
By somebody who works at the agency?

412
00:20:58,020 --> 00:21:00,540
本尼特先生的老熟人  是的
A longtime acquaintance of Mr. Bennett, yes.

413
00:21:03,530 --> 00:21:05,090
那你想让我做些什么
So what do you want from me?

414
00:21:05,220 --> 00:21:06,810
确认一下这个报告
Confirm the report.

415
00:21:07,430 --> 00:21:08,400
本尼特先生需要知道
Mr. Bennett needs to know

416
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,590
哪一部分业务处于调查之中
what part of the business is under investigation

417
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:12,780
以及他能做些什么以求自保
and what he can do to protect himself.

418
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:16,630
那可不容易
That's not going to be easy.

419
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:19,090
这么做的话不可能不让人察觉
Not without setting off alarm bells.

420
00:21:19,190 --> 00:21:20,380
你会想办法搞定的
You'll figure something out.

421
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:21,630
让我想办法吗
I'll figure something out?

422
00:21:21,630 --> 00:21:23,400
而且显然你的时间有限
And obviously there's a clock on this.

423
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,750
显然极了
Obviously.

424
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:55,710
喂
Hello?

425
00:21:56,170 --> 00:21:57,170
见效了
It's on.

426
00:21:57,590 --> 00:21:58,410
跟我说说
Tell me.

427
00:21:58,410 --> 00:21:59,360
我刚跟富兰克林见过面
I just met with Franklin.

428
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:00,820
他们开始慌了
They're panicking over there.

429
00:22:00,820 --> 00:22:01,940
让他们慌吧
Well, let them.

430
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:03,980
等满24小时
Wait 24 hours...

431
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:07,630
然后用我们知道炸弹袭击者的消息给他们一击
then hit them with the news we know who the bomber is.

432
00:22:08,120 --> 00:22:09,100
好的
Will do.

433
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:11,480
索尔
Uh, Saul?

434
00:22:11,630 --> 00:22:12,570
什么
Yeah?

435
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:15,960
在那之前我需要一点私人时间
I need some personal time between then and now.

436
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:17,390
行
You got it.

437
00:22:17,610 --> 00:22:19,300
-谢谢  -你没事吧
- Thanks. - You all right?

438
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:21,550
没事
Yeah.

439
00:22:21,930 --> 00:22:24,660
我应该早些告诉你布洛迪的情报
I should've shared that intel about Brody with you sooner.

440
00:22:24,660 --> 00:22:26,240
抱歉  我没考虑周全
I'm sorry, I wasn't thinking.

441
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:27,840
你死里逃生
You've been to hell and back.

442
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:29,640
我知道这对你有多重要
I know how important this is to you.

443
00:22:30,340 --> 00:22:33,400
我欠你的  我们都欠你的
I owe you. We all do.

444
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:36,140
只要我们找到真正的炸弹袭击者...
Yeah, well, as long as we get the real bomber...

445
00:22:36,140 --> 00:22:37,160
我们会的
We will.

446
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:52,180
是卡莉吗
Carrie?

447
00:22:52,180 --> 00:22:53,920
是  你怎么知道的
Yeah. How'd you know?

448
00:22:54,020 --> 00:22:55,010
你的语气
Tone of your voice.

449
00:22:55,010 --> 00:22:56,830
你从不和其他人那么说话
You don't talk to anyone else like that.

450
00:22:56,830 --> 00:22:58,750
我都没注意到
Huh, I wasn't aware.

451
00:22:59,470 --> 00:23:00,680
准备开饭吗
You ready to eat?

452
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:04,320
要不要开瓶酒
Should I open a bottle of wine?

453
00:23:04,930 --> 00:23:06,350
好主意
That's a great idea.

454
00:23:09,170 --> 00:23:10,130
听着
Listen...

455
00:23:10,130 --> 00:23:12,160
我得离开几天
I got to go away for a few days.

456
00:23:13,040 --> 00:23:14,080
是吗
You do?

457
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:15,600
-是的  -什么时候
- Yeah. - When?

458
00:23:15,850 --> 00:23:17,060
明天
Tomorrow.

459
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:19,870
索尔
Saul...

460
00:23:19,870 --> 00:23:21,050
我知道
I know.

461
00:23:22,370 --> 00:23:23,800
时机不太好
The timing's not great.

462
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:26,260
但你说只是几天对吗
But you said only a couple of days?

463
00:23:26,260 --> 00:23:29,460
对  顶多一周
Yeah. A week, at the most.

464
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:31,940
一周
A week?

465
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,180
要不是我非去不可
I wouldn't be going...

466
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:39,590
我也不会走的
if I didn't absolutely have to.

467
00:23:40,470 --> 00:23:42,300
我可以跟你一起去
You know what, I could go with you.

468
00:23:42,300 --> 00:23:44,120
-那可真是太棒了  -谁说不是呢
- Wouldn't that be great? - Why not?

469
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:46,000
这不是什么旅行
It's not that kind of trip.

470
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:47,910
虽然我希望是
I wish it were.

471
00:23:55,170 --> 00:23:56,470
-干杯  -干杯
- Cheers. - Cheers.

472
00:23:57,650 --> 00:23:58,910
为我们
To us.

473
00:24:05,580 --> 00:24:06,960
你觉得恶心想吐吗
You've been nauseous?

474
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,020
是的
Yeah.

475
00:24:08,020 --> 00:24:09,870
一般来说现在应该已经没那感觉了
Usually that goes away by now.

476
00:24:10,210 --> 00:24:11,510
我也是这么听说的
So I've heard.

477
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:15,210
我这里看的非常清楚
I'm getting a real clear image here.

478
00:24:15,920 --> 00:24:17,760
你想知道是男孩还是女孩吗
You want to know if it's a boy or a girl?

479
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,040
不想
No.

480
00:24:32,590 --> 00:24:34,010
很抱歉最后才来找你
Sorry this is so last-minute.

481
00:24:34,010 --> 00:24:36,050
不  很高兴见到你
No, no, it's great to see you.

482
00:24:36,650 --> 00:24:38,210
真是个惊喜
This is quite a surprise.

483
00:24:38,210 --> 00:24:39,670
上周我还在院里见到了麦琪
I saw Maggie at the hospital last week,

484
00:24:39,670 --> 00:24:41,110
她什么都没提
she didn't say a thing.

485
00:24:41,220 --> 00:24:42,530
她不知道
She doesn't know.

486
00:24:43,130 --> 00:24:44,390
这跟你为什么第13周
Does that have anything to do with

487
00:24:44,390 --> 00:24:46,790
才来做第一次孕检有关系吗
why you're coming in for your first prenatal exam

488
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:51,190
其实我没打算要孩子
I didn't exactly plan this.

489
00:24:51,790 --> 00:24:54,300
但你知道自己怀孕  已经有一阵子了吧
But you've known for some time.

490
00:24:57,690 --> 00:24:58,810
用药情况如何
What about medications?

491
00:24:58,810 --> 00:25:00,340
你现在在服用哪些药
What are you currently taking?

492
00:25:00,450 --> 00:25:02,450
现在什么药都没吃
Uh, at the moment, nothing.

493
00:25:02,650 --> 00:25:03,880
我知道
I see.

494
00:25:04,890 --> 00:25:06,800
我孕前一个月服用过
I was on 1,800 milligrams of lithium

495
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:08,480
1800毫克的锂盐
for about a month there.

496
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:10,680
当时事情有点失控
Things were a little out of control.

497
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:12,580
更早之前
And, uh, before that,

498
00:25:13,300 --> 00:25:14,970
喝了很多酒
There was a lot of drinking.

499
00:25:15,610 --> 00:25:17,850
非常多
A... Lot.

500
00:25:19,220 --> 00:25:20,430
在你知道自己怀孕之后吗
After you knew?

501
00:25:22,980 --> 00:25:25,760
我还没想过要去弄一个育婴室
I haven't been painting a nursery,

502
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:27,180
就那么放在一边
just put it that way.

503
00:25:27,830 --> 00:25:30,060
你是告诉我  你想做人流吗
Are you telling me you wish to terminate?

504
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:33,360
我只想知道测试结果
I just want to know what the tests say.

505
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:34,830
是不是都还好
If things are okay.

506
00:25:37,530 --> 00:25:39,190
你缺铁
You're iron deficient.

507
00:25:39,190 --> 00:25:40,040
这个我们可以补回来
We can fix that.

508
00:25:40,050 --> 00:25:42,210
但是你的血压非常高
But your blood pressure's very high.

509
00:25:43,810 --> 00:25:46,780
我的工作压力非常大
I've been... really stressed at work.

510
00:25:46,790 --> 00:25:48,770
你真的应该放松一下
Well, you really should be taking it easy.

511
00:25:50,050 --> 00:25:51,590
是啊  我会试试看
Yeah, I'll try.

512
00:25:52,660 --> 00:25:54,410
卡莉  我们有办法
Carrie, we can manage this.

513
00:25:54,410 --> 00:25:56,130
保证你和宝宝的健康
Keep you and the baby healthy.

514
00:25:56,250 --> 00:25:58,140
并不神奇  只是一个过程
It's not magic, it's a process.

515
00:25:58,550 --> 00:26:00,680
如果你想要顺其自然  决定权在你
You want to leave it to chance, that's up to you.

516
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:02,810
否则你就需要改变下自己的行为习惯
Otherwise you need to modify your behavior.

517
00:26:02,870 --> 00:26:05,750
不是一周或是两周  或者方便的时候
Not in a week or two, or when it's convenient.

518
00:26:05,750 --> 00:26:07,140
而是现在
Now.

519
00:26:11,150 --> 00:26:13,570
我现在做的事和孩子父亲有关
What I'm doing, it has to do with the father.

520
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:15,340
我得把事情捋顺
I need to make some things right.

521
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:18,030
这关系到很多人
It matters to a lot of people.

522
00:26:18,560 --> 00:26:20,500
但这不一样的  卡莉
But this is different, Carrie.

523
00:26:20,780 --> 00:26:22,460
你现在已经不是自己一个人了
You're not on your own anymore.

524
00:26:42,980 --> 00:26:44,130
法拉
Fara?

525
00:26:44,130 --> 00:26:45,350
西拉吉
Sherazi?

526
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:47,160
你是哪位
And you are?

527
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:49,540
米切尔·克劳森总长办公室
Mitchell Clausen. From the I.G.'s office.

528
00:26:49,540 --> 00:26:50,600
什么总长
I.G.?

529
00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:51,910
总监察长
Inspector General.

530
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:53,680
我能进来吗
May I come in?

531
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:55,200
[波斯语]

532
00:26:55,730 --> 00:26:58,420
[波斯语]

533
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,640
这边请
This way.

534
00:27:05,380 --> 00:27:06,660
我可以给你弄点喝的吗
May I offer you something?

535
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:08,060
不用
I'm good. Um...

536
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,600
你连续两天打电话来请病假
You called in sick two days in a row.

537
00:27:09,600 --> 00:27:11,150
是怎么了呢
Is something the matter?

538
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:13,160
偏头痛
Migraines.

539
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:15,160
可是你昨天开车去上班了
Yet you drove into work yesterday.

540
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:16,720
对
Yes.

541
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:19,230
你就呆坐在停车场半个多小时
Where you sat in the parking lot for over half an hour

542
00:27:19,230 --> 00:27:22,190
还是决定走了
before deciding to leave again.

543
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:24,980
我那时候希望头疼能止住
I was hoping the headache would go away.

544
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:27,040
所以你才去了 
Is that why you then paid a visit

545
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:29,580
最近发生双尸案的
to 1426 Longhill Road,

546
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:32,250
长山路1426号吗
where the recent double murder happened?

547
00:27:33,030 --> 00:27:36,170
贝塞斯达警局记下了你的车牌号
The bethesda P.D. took down your license number.

548
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:42,110
警局为了调查这案子
The agency had to call in a lot of favors

549
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:44,140
召集了众多帮手
to close that investigation.

550
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:47,290
你到那儿去会产生严重后果
Your going over there jeopardized all that.

551
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:50,790
我想看看案发现场
I wanted to see where it happened.

552
00:27:52,610 --> 00:27:53,850
为什么
Why?

553
00:27:55,790 --> 00:27:57,300
我很不安
It upset me. I...

554
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,770
我因此烦乱不堪
I was upset by it.

555
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:05,230
贝伦森局长对你表示出了
Director Berenson has shown an unusual degree

556
00:28:05,230 --> 00:28:07,370
非同寻常的信任  西拉吉小姐
of confidence in you, Ms. Sherazi...

557
00:28:07,370 --> 00:28:09,710
对你委以国家级的重要任务
entrusted you with matters of national importance.

558
00:28:09,710 --> 00:28:11,000
那个我知道
I'm aware of that.

559
00:28:11,530 --> 00:28:13,340
但是你目前的心理状态
But your current state of mind

560
00:28:13,340 --> 00:28:14,780
使你对局长和中情局的忠诚度
makes your loyalty to him

561
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:18,080
都有待商榷
and to the agency a very live issue.

562
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,200
转告局长不用担心
Tell the director not to worry.

563
00:28:21,390 --> 00:28:22,660
我很好
I'm fine.

564
00:28:23,070 --> 00:28:24,700
明天上班的时候
You can tell him yourself.

565
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,830
你自己跟他说吧
When you come into work tomorrow.

566
00:28:28,570 --> 00:28:29,730
行
Yes.

567
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:43,880
贝伦森局长
Director Berenson?

568
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:49,360
这个贝伦森局长是谁
Who is this Director Berenson?

569
00:28:49,360 --> 00:28:50,610
他是我上司
My boss.

570
00:28:52,890 --> 00:28:54,700
他不是银行里的人吧
But he's no banker, is he?

571
00:28:56,250 --> 00:28:57,390
不是
No.

572
00:28:58,190 --> 00:29:00,040
你依旧执迷不悟是吧
You went ahead, didn't you?

573
00:29:00,710 --> 00:29:02,810
把我的话当耳旁风
In spite of everything I said?

574
00:29:02,810 --> 00:29:04,630
爸爸  发生了恐怖袭击
Baba, an attack happened.

575
00:29:04,630 --> 00:29:05,910
那又怎样
So what?

576
00:29:05,910 --> 00:29:07,170
这又不关你的事
It's none of your business.

577
00:29:07,180 --> 00:29:08,590
他们需要有国际金融背景
They needed Farsi speakers

578
00:29:08,590 --> 00:29:11,020
又懂波斯语的人
with experience in international finance.

579
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:12,680
我必须帮他们
I had to help.

580
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:14,310
要是那些伊朗特工
And when the secret police find out

581
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:16,510
发现你为美国人卖命  那怎么办
who you work for, what then?

582
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:19,160
我们在德黑兰还有家人
We have family still in Tehran!

583
00:29:19,210 --> 00:29:21,920
你的叔叔  婶婶  侄子
Your uncle, his wife and children.

584
00:29:22,380 --> 00:29:25,620
到时候全部都要上黑名单  被处以绞刑
They will be added to the list of those to be hanged,

585
